{"tid":1493119,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"連儂牆斬人 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2019-08-21T06:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T06:49:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71df784c1e98b0903f33a2923d659bf3623aa25d","tid":1493119,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20190821/20752634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F20752634&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9oiYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=00e593dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F20752634&h=799b5999\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20190821/20752634</a><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆斬人 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190821/large/1566296579_fc62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190821%2Flarge%2F1566296579_fc62.jpg&h=0772b295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒朋友去了台灣，發現台北也有連儂牆，最大特色是，有警員在現場看守。因為那幅牆由立委和團體正式向政府申請，取得許可，所以政府派警察看守，他們也知道連儂牆是容易引起政治爭拗的敏感地。<br />\n<br />\n警察看守台北的連儂牆，並不代表警察支持這些政治訴求；就等於社團老大出殯，警察一定會派員現場監視，因為擔心龍蛇混雜，易出亂子。當然，經過這個夏天，我們不能排除警察可能真心想去拜祭，畢竟並肩作戰嘛。<br />\n<br />\n香港的連儂牆就如許多香港的地區治安，都是「無警時分」，縱使連儂牆多次有縱火刑毀打鬥事情。<br />\n<br />\n最終由拳頭交變成刀刀見血，將軍澳連儂牆有街坊打扮的刀手斬人，行凶前還要和年青人搭訕交流政見，然後大喝一聲「我忍唔住」，出手斬人。<br />\n<br />\n凶徒深夜落樓帶有雙刀還要帶備衣物更換，如果是一時激憤行凶，難以置信。網上除了聲討凶徒，也多了許多「散步群組」，許多街坊自發組團落樓散步巡邏連儂牆，又呼籲市民落樓要呼朋引伴，又要孭背包裝厚雜誌保護自己&hellip;&hellip;香港已經淪落到市民落樓都要full gear才能散步的危險境地？所謂香港最安全城市的稱號，是否也像催淚彈一樣，過了期？<br />\n<br />\n最可怕不是刀手，而是權貴對刀手的回應。機場打環時記者事件，權貴上下左右如見血鯊魚，即時洶湧撲出開記招發聲明譴責，甚麼「人神共憤」、「超越道德底線」，就差一句「千古罪人」。但記者被打，梁金城被打，連儂牆斬人，權貴銷聲匿跡，政府發了一個虛偽聲明「譴責一切暴力」。為甚麼要譴責「一切」暴力？即是不敢單單就這宗個案表態？害怕譴責連儂牆的暴力便等於政府支持連儂牆嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\nBe water (李純恩)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n向多倫多的中國人致敬 (高慧然)"},{"pid":"88f3f67c16c9a3bba03b4758940de04df238a365","tid":1493119,"uid":229385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6jJoyp3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jJoyp3.jpg&h=7ed7a88d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/uvSwHez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSwHez.png&h=c21fa885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lyr9tRx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLyr9tRx.png&h=39eb00b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"bb65743d6bfcc6242a5273125a7756211ddf1727","tid":1493119,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T06:42:00.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvSwHez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvSwHez.png&h=660b03dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c153ef0e3f962002cb5dd8097526e7e874d9323","tid":1493119,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"